menu_items.name: Sausage Pizza
menu_items.description: Our signature pizza sauce layered with sausage and real cheese made from mozzarella for a taste you’ll crave. Your choice of crust.

menu_items.name: Pepperoni Pizza
menu_items.description: Your choice of crust covered with our signature pizza sauce, real cheese made from mozzarella, and pepperoni. With a pepperoni in almost every bite, it's one of our most popular pizzas.

menu_items.name: Cheese Pizza
menu_items.description: Simple, yet simply delicious. Real cheese made from mozzarella on top of our signature pizza sauce with your choice of crust, then baked to a golden brown. It has just what you want, and nothing you don’t.

menu_items.name: The Works Pizza
menu_items.description: It’s everything you want on a pizza – and then some. A heaping helping of pepperoni, julienne-cut Canadian bacon, spicy Italian sausage, fresh-cut onions, crisp green peppers, mushrooms, ripe black olives, and real cheese made from mozzarella. When you’re hungry for a hearty pizza, the Works always works.

menu_items.name: The Meats Pizza
menu_items.description: A masterpiece of hearty, high-quality meats including pepperoni, savory sausage, real beef, hickory-smoked bacon, and julienne-cut Canadian bacon, all topped with real cheese made from mozzarella.

menu_items.name: Garden Fresh Pizza
menu_items.description: All your favorite veggies together on a delightfully delicious pizza. Loaded with crisp green peppers, fresh-cut onions, mushrooms, ripe black olives, vine-ripened Roma tomatoes, and real cheese made from mozzarella.

menu_items.name: Super Hawaiian Pizza
menu_items.description: Get a taste of the tropics. This super delicious pizza is loaded with sweet, juicy pineapple tidbits, julienne-cut Canadian bacon, hickory-smoked bacon, a three-cheese blend, and real cheese made from mozzarella on our signature sauce and original fresh dough.

menu_items.name: Ultimate Pepperoni Pizza
menu_items.description: Just when you think our pepperoni pizza couldn’t get any tastier, we craft the ultimate masterpiece. Our original fresh dough is covered with signature pizza sauce, 30% more pepperoni than our traditional pie, a blend of Parmesan and Romano, and real cheese made from mozzarella, all sprinkled with classic Italian seasoning.

menu_items.name: Philly Cheesesteak Pizza
menu_items.description: Whether you’re a native Philadelphian or still waiting to visit the City of Brotherly Love, “youse” can enjoy an elevated form of the classic Philly cheesesteak in this original tribute to the king of hot sandwiches, the Papa John’s Philly Cheesesteak pizza. Considered by its fans to be one of the best Papa John’s pizza varieties, this meaty and cheesy triumph will keep the party going all night long. For a flavorful treat that would satisfy even the Philly Phanatic, try the Philly Cheesesteak pizza from Papa John’s.
